x640 ham mode:

00rrggbb load two pixels colors (x320 truъ color)

0101RRrr modify (XOR or ADD) color components of adjacent x640 pixels
0110RRgg
0111RRbb
1001GGrr
1010GGgg
1011GGbb
1101BBrr
1110BBgg
1111BBbb

